o brother , where art thou ? is a 2000 american drama film written and directed by joel coen . the film stars george clooney , ethan coen , ethan coen , and ethan coen . the film was written by joel coen and ethan coen . the film was released in the united states on may 5 , 2000 . the film was nominated for the academy award for best foreign language film , but was not accepted as a nominee .